# Session start

1. Read `HANDOFF.md` first
2. Read `AGENTS.md` and `README.md` priorities
3. Read relevant `src/modules/<module>/README.md`
4. Work on one module per session
5. State which build-priority item the task serves

# Before each action

Consult `HANDOFF.md`, then `AGENTS.md`, then `README.md` priorities before code, docs, commands, git, or review work.

# After each action

Update `HANDOFF.md` **Live session state** after every completed action. Append `README.md` Ordered Build Record when behavior changed.

# Session end

1. Run `npm run lint && npm run type-check && npm run test`
2. Commit and push to GitHub
3. Update `HANDOFF.md` live session state and session log
4. Append `README.md` Ordered Build Record if behavior changed

# Handoff rule

Never switch between Cursor and Codex with uncommitted work. Update `HANDOFF.md` first.
